    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "image",
              "identifier": "media-2929807",
              "metadata": {
                "anchor": "2929807",
                "title": "Figure 1",
                "abstract": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "A box and its properties"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Define the shape of the box in the x-, y-, and z-axis dimensions of its local coordinate space by setting its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox/1523898-width"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox/1522901-height"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox/1523514-length"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " properties. Add rounded edges and corners to a box with its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox/1523302-chamferradius"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. To position and orient a box in a scene, attach it to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnnode/1407966-geometry"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property of an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnnode"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Control the level of detail with the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox/1523559-widthsegmentcount"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox/1522869-heightsegmentcount"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox/1523721-lengthsegmentcount"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox/1522976-chamfersegmentcount"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " properties. A higher segment count produces more vertices, which can improve rendering quality for certain lighting models or custom shader effects, but at a cost to rendering performance."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can assign up to six "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnmaterial"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instances to a box—one for each side—with its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scngeometry/1523472-materials"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnbox"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " class automatically creates "
            },
            {
